# UptimeStatusProbe - Endpoint Health Monitor

UptimeStatusProbe is useful for quickly validating API uptime and performance over time.

## Features
- Logs HTTP status and latency  
- Pings multiple endpoints  
- CLI-friendly  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_UptimeStatusProbe.git
cd 37_UptimeStatusProbe
python monitor.py
